Interface Stub

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ReferencedBoundElement, ReferencedEnd, RegularEnd, URNmodelElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StubImpl

    public interface Stub
extends URNmodelElement, RegularEnd, ReferencedEnd
    A representation of the model object 'Stub'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Stub Type
    • Index
    • Name
    • Long Name
    • Params
    • Stub Ref
    • Out Paths
    • Connecting Stub Body
